{
  "stem": "26142.17",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I think, by that time, some Frenchmen, French doctors, they were getting some packages through the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they had some-- some medicine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So they were giving him some painkillers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And-- and-- all-- everybody attended to this general.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How he got-- how he lost his leg, I didn't-- he didn't-- he didn't tell me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But one day-- one day the-- the head commander of the-- of the camp, in Hersbruck, came in, into the revier.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what rank he had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he came right over to this French general, and he said to him, [SPEAKING GERMAN] He says, good morning, my colleague.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How are you doing?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this French general turns around and in a fine, perfect German, [SPEAKING GERMAN] You-- you dirty pig!",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I am not your colleague!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I heard this general telling so, I figured he is probably going to shoot him right-- right here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This commander, the German commander from that, he turned right around, and he walked right out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't say a word to this-- to this Frenchman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, this Frenchman, he lived a few more days, and-- and he-- he passed away in the night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was in very big, big pain.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was-- he was crying and-- and-- and he died.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But what happened was that the doctor that operated on me, because they knew that this is coming to an end, and he was doing just like in a butcher shop.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All he-- all he had is scissors and knives and-- and a table.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he had nothing else that he could give to people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Cutting off limbs and-- and-- and-- and opening up wounds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And somebody-- somebody-- that doctor that was over him, came in just a day before.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
